content: प्रचुर {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Much, ample, abundant, plentiful; नित्यव्यया प्रचुरनित्यधनागमा च <ls>Bh. 2. 47</ls>; <ls>Śi. 12. 72.</ls> {@--2@} Great, large, extensive; प्रचुरपुरंदरधनुः <ls>Gīt. 2.</ls> {@--3@} (At the end of <ab>comp.</ab>) Abounding in, filled or replete with. --रः A thief.
